#: accounting/models.py:573
msgid "Payment Instructions:"
msgstr "Zahlungsanweisungen:"

#: accounting/models.py:595
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Your Invoice for Order {order_id} - {site_name}"
msgstr "Ihre Rechnung für die Bestellung {order_id} – {site_name}"

#: accounting/models.py:596
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Dear Customer,\n"
"\n"
"Thank you for your purchase! You can find the invoice of your ticket "
"purchase attached.\n"
"\n"
"Please find your tickets and purchase details under the following link:\n"
"\n"
"{order_link}\n"
"\n"
"We look forward to seeing you at the event.\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"The Event Team"
msgstr ""
"Sehr geehrter Kunde,\n"
"\n"
"Vielen Dank für Ihren Einkauf! Sie finden die Rechnung Ihres Ticketkaufs im "
"Anhang.\n"
"\n"
"Ihre Tickets und Kaufdetails finden Sie unter folgendem Link:\n"
"\n"
"{order_link}\n"
"\n"
"Wir freuen uns darauf, Sie bei der Veranstaltung zu sehen.\n"
"\n"
"Mit freundlichen Grüßen\n"
"Das Event-Team"

#: accounting/models.py:647
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Payment Instructions for Your Order {order_id} on {site_name}"
msgstr "Zahlungsanweisungen für Ihre Bestellung {order_id} auf {site_name}"

#: accounting/models.py:649
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Dear Customer,\n"
"\n"
"Thank you for your purchase! Please find the payment instructions for your "
"order below.\n"
"\n"
"{payment_instructions}\n"
"\n"
"You can view your order details here: {order_link}\n"
"\n"
"We look forward to seeing you at the event.\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"The Event Team"
msgstr ""
"Sehr geehrter Kunde,\n"
"\n"
"Vielen Dank für Ihren Einkauf! Nachfolgend finden Sie die "
"Zahlungsanweisungen für Ihre Bestellung.\n"
"\n"
"{payment_instructions}\n"
"\n"
"Sie können Ihre Bestelldetails hier ansehen: {order_link}\n"
"\n"
"Wir freuen uns, Sie auf der Veranstaltung begrüßen zu dürfen.\n"
"\n"
"Viele Grüße,\n"
"Das Event-Team"

#: accounting/models.py:708
#, python-brace-format
msgid "New Order {order_id} on {site_name}"
msgstr "Neue Bestellung {order_id} auf {site_name}"

#: accounting/models.py:709
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Dear Ticket Master,\n"
"\n"
"A new order has been placed on {site_name}.\n"
"\n"
"Please find the order details below:\n"
"\n"
"Order ID: {order_id}\n"
"Order Date: {order_date}\n"
"Customer: {customer_name}\n"
"Customer Email: {customer_email}\n"
"Total Amount: {total_amount} {currency}\n"
"\n"
"You can view the order details here: {order_link}\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"The Event Team"
msgstr ""
"Sehr geehrter Ticketmaster,\n"
"\n"
"Eine neue Bestellung wurde auf {site_name} aufgegeben.\n"
"\n"
"Die Bestelldetails finden Sie unten:\n"
"\n"
"Bestell-ID: {order_id}\n"
"Bestelldatum: {order_date}\n"
"Kunde: {customer_name}\n"
"Kunden-E-Mail: {customer_email}\n"
"Gesamtbetrag: {total_amount} {currency}\n"
"\n"
"Sie können die Bestelldetails hier einsehen: {order_link}\n"
"\n"
"Mit freundlichen Grüßen\n"
"Das Event-Team"

#: accounting/models.py:762
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Your Order {order_id} has been Refunded or Cancelled - {site_name}"
msgstr ""
"Ihre Bestellung {order_id} wurde erstattet oder storniert - {site_name}"

#: accounting/models.py:763
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Dear Customer,\n"
"\n"
"We regret to inform you that your order with ID {order_id} has been refunded "
"or cancelled.\n"
"\n"
"If you have already transferred the payment the amount of {total_amount} "
"{currency} will be returned to your original payment method "
"({payment_method}).\n"
"\n"
"Please note that it may take a few business days for the refund to be "
"processed and reflected in your account, depending on your bank or payment "
"provider.\n"
"\n"
"If you have any questions or concerns regarding this refund or cancellation, "
"please do not hesitate to contact our support team.\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"The Event Team"
msgstr ""
"Sehr geehrter Kunde,\n"
"\n"
"Wir bedauern Ihnen mitteilen zu müssen, dass Ihre Bestellung mit der ID "
"{order_id} zurückerstattet oder storniert wurde.\n"
"\n"
"Wenn Sie die Zahlung bereits überwiesen haben, wird der Betrag von "
"{total_amount} {currency} auf Ihre ursprüngliche Zahlungsmethode "
"({payment_method}) zurückgebucht.\n"
"\n"
"Bitte beachten Sie, dass es je nach Bank oder Zahlungsanbieter einige "
"Werktage dauern kann, bis die Rückerstattung bearbeitet und in Ihrem Konto "
"verbucht wird.\n"
"\n"
"Wenn Sie Fragen oder Bedenken zu dieser Rückerstattung oder Stornierung "
"haben, zögern Sie bitte nicht, unser Support-Team zu kontaktieren.\n"
"\n"
"Mit freundlichen Grüßen,\n"
"Das Event-Team"

#: accounting/models.py:816
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Order {order_id} has been Refunded or Cancelled on {site_name}"
msgstr "Bestellung {order_id} wurde auf {site_name} erstattet oder storniert."

#: accounting/models.py:817
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Dear Ticket Master,\n"
"\n"
"We inform you that the order with ID {order_id} has been refunded or "
"cancelled.\n"
"\n"
"Please find the order details below:\n"
"\n"
"Order ID: {order_id}\n"
"Order Date: {order_date}\n"
"Customer: {customer_name}\n"
"Customer Email: {customer_email}\n"
"Total Amount: {total_amount} {currency}\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,\n"
"The Event Team"
msgstr ""
"Sehr geehrte Ticketmaster-Mitarbeiter,\n"
"\n"
"wir informieren Sie darüber, dass die Bestellung mit der ID {order_id} "
"storniert bzw. erstattet wurde.\n"
"\n"
"Die Bestelldetails finden Sie unten:\n"
"\n"
"Bestell-ID: {order_id}\n"
"Bestelldatum: {order_date}\n"
"Kunde: {customer_name}\n"
"E-Mail-Adresse des Kunden: {customer_email}\n"
"Gesamtbetrag: {total_amount} {currency}\n"
"\n"
"Mit freundlichen Grüßen\n"
"Ihr Event-Team"

#: accounting/models.py:857
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Cannot refund or cancel order: order is not in CONFIRMED or PREAUTH status. "
